{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bede8c1726","title":"关于军队整训的指示——给林彪同志的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3bc61be728","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":7,"articleId":"bede8c1726"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"68bc1dc2e3","name":"三支两军","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8aea2767eb","type":"paragraph","text":"同意。团结和服从都是有条件的，不是无条件的。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"6e56a8c042","type":"paragraph","text":"年纪大的、年纪中的、年纪小的也要“三结合”，不要看不起年轻人。二十几岁、三十儿岁的人都能做工作。搞“三结合”，要老中小，老的都会去见上帝的。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"513d14862c","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。批制文章文字要短。彭、罗、陆杨可以提为反革命修正主义，其他人都称修正主义分子。中国的赫鲁晓夫在文章中提，在标题上要提。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"8e6f08b259","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"8684ce1c1c","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"c56b5c994e","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"21157b7628","type":"paragraph","text":"大批制要旗重，要确实，要调查清楚。调查清楚，批制才有力量，否期就会一风吹。引他（指刘少奇）的不能只顾头不顾尾。批制要站得佳。“托拉斯”这个名词，不能一概敏，主要他走本主义道路。有些旧名词要赋予新的意义。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"a0d2ab1cd1","type":"paragraph","text":"“聊服工具论”要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律。服从、团结，那是有条件的。今年形势好，布、粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"bf55e70772","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、罗、陆、杨可以称为“反革命修正主义分子”，其他人称“修正主义分子”。“中国的赫鲁晓夫，”文章中提，在标题上不要提。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"4a614d0857","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"a80ccec992","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"3a951fbfe9","type":"paragraph","text":"X写文章要琢磨，要准确，要尖锐明确。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"931a8cf404","type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年9月）关于军队整凯的指示","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"25d72b5378","type":"paragraph","text":"船林彪同志的信","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"389e9d8fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月七日）林彪同志。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"c068f2f30c","type":"paragraph","text":"各地军队都应整训一个短时期，时间10-—14天为宜，已经整训过的，一个月或三个月再整训一次，全军三支两军人员，每一个月或两个月，都应整训一次，发扬成绩，纠正错课，以利再战。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"9fd91960f7","type":"paragraph","text":"对广州、湖南军区报告的批示","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"36e542d03b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年）一、现将广州、湖南军区报告两个文件，发给你们希望避照执行。","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"cb825c3188","type":"paragraph","text":"二、是错澳的必须改正，如果不改正，越陷越深，到头来还得改正，威信损失就大了。及卓改正威信只能比以前高。","index":18,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"49669e9593","type":"paragraph","text":"三、不能动动摇接，犹犹豫豫，听老婆孩子从保守派那里来的错澳，信以为具。","index":19,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"},{"id":"c6aa5dfaa4","type":"paragraph","text":"·307。","index":20,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726"}],"page":{"id":"17fa7c73e0","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bede8c1726","start":320,"end":320}}}},"__N_SSG":true}